Description: Welcoming a new baby gives you the chance to revamp your closet – and a new bag is the easiest place to start. The Highline by Skip Hop collection has reinvented the diaper bag for women who refuse to compromise personal style and much-needed function. Our Convertible Diaper bag is an instant conversation piece. A statement silhouette that can be worn as a Crossbody, converted to a Backpack, or carried by its Tote handles, the Convertible Diaper Bag is everything you need and the ultimate find. No one will know it’s a diaper bag and your other mommy-friends will want one once they figure it out.
